The tools directory contains the following:

---++ a quick BuildContrib based TWikiRelease builder
   * build.pl
      * running 'perl build.pl release' should result in TWiki.txt, TWiki.tgz and TWiki.zip
   * DEPENDENCIES
   * MANIFEST
---++ documentation extractor and generator
   * addpod.pl
   * gendocs.pl
---++ a full TWikiFor builder and installer
   * builddistros.pl
   * distro
---++ various tools to help configure TWiki
   * fixHtaccess.pl
   * mklinks.pl
   * perlmod2www.pl
   * plugins_conformance_analyser.pl
   * rewriteshbang.pl
   * unisonsync.pl
   * upgradeformat
---++ packaging info and scripts for various distributions
   * pkg
